      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『Grab the BIG4』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――『Grab the BIG4』",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――トーナメント初戦後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the First Tournament Match",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.0466666136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、愛。今日のステージ、お疲れ様\n急ごしらえの三人体制としては上出来よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ Ai. Good job‚ on today's stage\nWe did a great job considering our hastily assembled three-person lineup",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.0666662891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい～！　自分が頑張らないとって\nつい力が入り過ぎて、気が付いたら走っちゃってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry~! I think to try my best\nI got too worked up and ended up running before I realized it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "こころも気合いが入り過ぎちゃいまして……\n慣れないことはするものじゃありませんね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro was too fired up too…\nI shouldn't do things I'm not used to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6282536228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.8666659077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "不慣れな三人体制なんだから仕方ないわ\n私だっていい出来じゃなかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can't be helped‚ since we're an unfamiliar three-person team\nI didn't do very well either",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.9333325744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "……こころ。なんだか今日の莉央さん、凄く優しいね\n私達がミスをしたのに、全然怒らないなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Kokoro. Rio-san seems really kind today\nShe didn't get angry at us even though we made misses",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4160660408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.6666659077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "おかしいですね。いつもの反省会だと\nネチネチネチネチ私達が泣くまでミスを責めるのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's strange. At our usual debriefing meeting‚\nshe grumble and grumble about our misses until we cry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666661581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.1333328287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、聞こえてるわよ。それとこころ、嘘を\n織り交ぜないでちょうだい。……あら、誰か来たわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can hear you two. And Kokoro‚ please don't\nmake a lie. …Oh‚ someone's here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7999994915,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7233.333329400004,
          "startTime": 55.3666661581
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0999994953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "天動です。一回戦、お疲れ様でした\nお邪魔してもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's Tendou. Did a great job‚ in the first round\nMay I come in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.1422444065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "……こころ、お説教は後でね\n大丈夫よ、瑠依。入ってちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Kokoro‚ I'll give you a lecture later\nIt's okay‚ Rui. Come in",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0422444027,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3515.4587427999927,
          "startTime": 72.5577031455
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2957.755088799999,
          "startTime": 71.9999994915
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.8089110732
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.6999994915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、失礼します。莉央さん、こころ、愛\nまずは二回戦進出、おめでとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ excuse me. Rio-san‚ Kokoro‚ Ai\nFirst of all‚ congratulations on advancing to the second round",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.271814096
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ギリギリの勝利だったけどね\n貴方達も、二回戦進出おめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it was a close victory\nCongratulations to you guys on advancing to the second round",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8384807588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.0051474293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。お互い、このまま順調に\n勝ち進めば、セミファイナルでぶつかりますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. If both sides keep going at this pace‚\nwe'll face each other in the semifinals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4999994915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.0421995839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "私達、優勝候補だものね。他のグループには悪いけど\nここが事実上の決勝戦になるでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're‚ the favorites to win. I'm sorry to the other groups‚\nbut but this is practically the final",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4755329134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.5421975494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYでは、あと一歩及ばなかったけど……\n今度は私達が勝たせてもらうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We fell just short in I-UNITY…\nThis time‚ we're going to win",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0421995801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.6755380035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……そのことなんですけど、莉央さん\n失礼を承知でお願いがあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…About that‚ Rio-san\nI know this is rude‚ but I have a favor to ask",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3333399456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.8992094398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "もし準決勝で私達と戦うことになったら――その時は\n葵さんも加えた四人で、私達と戦ってもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're to fight us in the semifinals―― then‚\nwith Aoi-san added‚ would you be able to fight us as a four-person team?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2666712444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.0189833046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どうして瑠依さんがそんなことを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Why would Rui-san say that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0189833046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.252312569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、愛。気分を悪くするわよね\n三人の力を軽視している訳じゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ Ai. I made you feel bad\nI'm not underestimating the power of these three people",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2000045777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.4212717098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今のLizNoirからは\nI-UNITYで対戦した時の怖さは、感じない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ LizNoir\nI don't feel the fear I felt when we fought in I-UNITY",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7333399456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.1374172253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_08_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "最初のうちは、三人体制という物めずらしさで\nポイントを稼ぐことが出来るでしょうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the beginning‚ it may be possible to earn points\nwith a rare three-person formation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6666732789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
